{{ 'privacy-opt-out.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

<div
  style="
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: #f4f5f7;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  "
>
  <header style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e4e0; background: #f4f5f7">
    <div style="max-width: 688px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px 24px">
      <a
        href="/ "
        aria-label="Revive home "
        style="
          display: inline-block;
          font:
            600 15px/1 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
            sans-serif;
          letter-spacing: 0.24em;
          text-transform: uppercase;
          color: #1a211e;
          text-decoration: none;
        "
        >REVIVE</a
      >
    </div>
  </header>
  <main
    style="
      flex: 1 0 auto;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 688px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: clamp(30px, 5vw, 52px) 24px 64px;
    "
  >
    <h1
      style="
        font:
          600 clamp(29px, 7vw, 40px)/1.12 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
          sans-serif;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        color: #1a211e;
        margin: 0 0 20px;
        text-wrap: balance;
      "
    >
      Do Not Sell or Share My Personal Information
    </h1>
    <p
      style="
        font:
          400 clamp(16px, 4vw, 17px)/1.6 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
          sans-serif;
        color: #2c332f;
        margin: 0;
        text-wrap: pretty;
        max-width: 60ch;
      "
    >
      Revive Teeth does not sell your personal information for money. We do share certain data with advertising
      partners, including Meta, for advertising purposes, which may be considered a 'sale' or 'share' under some state
      privacy laws. This page lets you opt out of that sharing and exercise your other privacy rights.
    </p>
    <div
      aria-hidden="true "
      style="height: 1px; background: #e2e4e0; margin: 36px 0"
    ></div>
    <section aria-labelledby="gpc-heading ">
      <span
        style="
          display: block;
          font:
            600 12px/1 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
            sans-serif;
          letter-spacing: 0.16em;
          text-transform: uppercase;
          color: #1b2d5c;
          margin: 0 0 12px;
        "
        >Automatic</span
      >
      <div
        style="
          background: #ffffff;
          border: 1px solid #e2e4e0;
          border-radius: 12px;
          padding: 22px;
          box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(20, 33, 28, 0.04);
        "
      >
        <div
          style="
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
          "
        >
          <h2
            id="gpc-heading "
            style="
              font:
                600 20px/1.3 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
                sans-serif;
              letter-spacing: -0.01em;
              color: #1a211e;
              margin: 0;
            "
          >
            Using a privacy-enabled browser?
          </h2>
          <div
            value="{{ gpcActive }}"
          >
            <span
              style="
                display: inline-flex;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 7px;
                font:
                  500 12px/1 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
                  sans-serif;
                color: #12213f;
                background: #eaeef6;
                border: 1px solid #c7d3e8;
                border-radius: 999px;
                padding: 6px 11px;
              "
            >
              <span
                style="
                  width: 7px;
                  height: 7px;
                  border-radius: 999px;
                  background: #1b2d5c;
                  flex: none;
                "
              ></span
              >Signal detected, opt out applied</span
            >
          </div>
          <div
            value="{{ gpcNotActive }} "
          >
            <span
              style="
                display: inline-flex;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 7px;
                font:
                  500 12px/1 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
                  sans-serif;
                color: #656b67;
                background: transparent;
                border: 1px solid #d3d6d1;
                border-radius: 999px;
                padding: 6px 11px;
              "
            >
              GPC supported</span
            >
          </div>
        </div>
        <p
          style="
            font:
              400 15px/1.6 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
              sans-serif;
            color: #353b37;
            margin: 0;
            max-width: 62ch;
          "
        >
          We honor Global Privacy Control (GPC) signals. If your browser sends a GPC signal, your opt-out from the sale
          or sharing of data collected by cookies and pixels on this site is applied automatically. No form needed.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <div
      aria-hidden="true "
      style="height: 1px; background: #e2e4e0; margin: 36px 0"
    ></div>
    <section aria-labelledby="device-heading ">
      <span
        style="
          display: block;
          font:
            600 12px/1 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
            sans-serif;
          letter-spacing: 0.16em;
          text-transform: uppercase;
          color: #1b2d5c;
          margin: 0 0 12px;
        "
        >This browser</span
      >
      <h2
        id="device-heading "
        style="
          font:
            600 21px/1.3 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
            sans-serif;
          letter-spacing: -0.01em;
          color: #1a211e;
          margin: 0 0 12px;
        "
      >
        Opt out on this device
      </h2>
      <div id="optout-section">
        <div>
          <p
            style="
              font:
                400 16px/1.6 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
                sans-serif;
              color: #353b37;
              margin: 0 0 18px;
              max-width: 60ch;
            "
          >
            Click below to opt out of the sharing of data collected by cookies and advertising pixels in this browser.
          </p>
          <button
            type="button "
            id="optout-button"
          >
            Opt out of sale or sharing
          </button>
          <p
            style="
              font:
                400 13px/1.55 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
                sans-serif;
              color: #656b67;
              margin: 12px 0 0;
              max-width: 60ch;
            "
          >
            This applies to this browser and device. If you use another browser or clear cookies, repeat this step or
            submit the form below.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        id="success-section"
        hidden
      >
        <div
          id="optout-confirm "
          tabindex="-1 "
          role="status "
          aria-live="polite "
          style="
            background: #eaeef6;
            border: 1px solid #c7d3e8;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 22px;
            animation: revEnter 0.25s ease both;
            outline: none;
          "
        >
          <div
            aria-hidden="true "
            style="
              display: inline-flex;
              align-items: center;
              justify-content: center;
              width: 30px;
              height: 30px;
              border-radius: 999px;
              background: #1b2d5c;
              color: #ffffff;
              font:
                700 15px/1 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
                sans-serif;
              margin-bottom: 12px;
            "
          >
            ✓
          </div>
          <h3
            style="
              font:
                600 18px/1.3 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
                sans-serif;
              color: #1a211e;
              margin: 0 0 8px;
            "
          >
            You're opted out on this browser.
          </h3>
          <p
            style="
              font:
                400 15px/1.6 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
                sans-serif;
              color: #353b37;
              margin: 0;
              max-width: 60ch;
            "
          >
            This applies to this browser and device. If you use another browser or clear cookies, repeat this step or
            submit the form below.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <div
      aria-hidden="true "
      style="height: 1px; background: #e2e4e0; margin: 36px 0"
    ></div>
    <section aria-labelledby="form-heading ">
      <span
        style="
          display: block;
          font:
            600 12px/1 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
            sans-serif;
          letter-spacing: 0.16em;
          text-transform: uppercase;
          color: #1b2d5c;
          margin: 0 0 12px;
        "
        >Your account and order data</span
      >
      <h2
        id="form-heading "
        style="
          font:
            600 21px/1.3 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
            sans-serif;
          letter-spacing: -0.01em;
          color: #1a211e;
          margin: 0 0 12px;
        "
      >
        Submit a privacy request
      </h2>
      <div value="{{ showForm }} ">
        <div>
          <p
            style="
              font:
                400 16px/1.6 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
                sans-serif;
              color: #353b37;
              margin: 0 0 6px;
              max-width: 60ch;
            "
          >
            To opt out of sharing tied to your customer record, or to exercise your other rights, submit this form. We
            respond to verifiable requests within 45 days.
          </p>
          <p
            style="
              font:
                400 13px/1.5 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
                sans-serif;
              color: #656b67;
              margin: 0 0 22px;
            "
          >
            Fields marked with an asterisk are required.
          </p>
          <form
            sc-camel-no-validate="{{ yes }} "
            sc-camel-on-submit="{{ onSubmit }} "
          >
            <div style="margin-bottom: 20px">
              <label
                for="pr-name "
                style="
                  display: block;
                  font:
                    600 14px/1.35 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
                    sans-serif;
                  color: #1a211e;
                  margin: 0 0 7px;
                "
                >Full name <span aria-hidden="true " style="color: #1b2d5c">*</span></label
              >
              <input
                id="pr-name "
                name="full_name "
                type="text "
                autocomplete="name "
                aria-required="true "
                aria-invalid="{{ ariaName }} "
                aria-describedby="pr-name-err "
                sc-camel-on-change="{{ onName }} "
                style="
                  display: block;
                  width: 100%;
                  font:
                    400 16px/1.4 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
                    sans-serif;
                  color: #1a211e;
                  background: #ffffff;
                  border: 1px solid #cfd3ce;
                  border-radius: 8px;
                  padding: 13px 14px;
                "
                style-focus="{ borderColor:'#1B2D5C', boxShadow:'0 0 0 3px rgba(27,45,92,0.18)' } "
              />
              <div
                value="{{ errName }} "
              >
                <p
                  id="pr-name-err"
                  class="error"
                  role="alert "
                  style="
                    font:
                      500 13px/1.45 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
                      sans-serif;
                    color: #b42318;
                    margin: 7px 0 0;
                  "
                >
                  {{ errName }}
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-bottom: 20px">
              <label
                for="pr-email "
                style="
                  display: block;
                  font:
                    600 14px/1.35 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
                    sans-serif;
                  color: #1a211e;
                  margin: 0 0 7px;
                "
                >Email address <span aria-hidden="true " style="color: #1b2d5c">*</span></label
              >
              <input
                id="pr-email "
                name="email "
                type="email "
                inputmode="email "
                autocomplete="email "
                aria-required="true "
                aria-invalid="{{ ariaEmail }} "
                aria-describedby="pr-email-help pr-email-err "
                value="{{ emailVal }} "
                sc-camel-on-change="{{ onEmail }} "
                style="
                  display: block;
                  width: 100%;
                  font:
                    400 16px/1.4 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
                    sans-serif;
                  color: #1a211e;
                  background: #ffffff;
                  border: 1px solid #cfd3ce;
                  border-radius: 8px;
                  padding: 13px 14px;
                "
                style-focus="{ borderColor:'#1B2D5C', boxShadow:'0 0 0 3px rgba(27,45,92,0.18)' } "
              />
              <p
                id="pr-email-help "
                style="
                  font:
                    400 13px/1.45 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
                    sans-serif;
                  color: #656b67;
                  margin: 7px 0 0;
                "
              >
                Use the email associated with your order, if you have one.
              </p>
              <div
                value="{{ errEmail }} "
              >
                <p
                  id="pr-email-err "
                  role="alert "
                  style="
                    font:
                      500 13px/1.45 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
                      sans-serif;
                    color: #b42318;
                    margin: 7px 0 0;
                  "
                >
                  {{ errEmail }}
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-bottom: 20px">
              <label
                for="pr-state "
                style="
                  display: block;
                  font:
                    600 14px/1.35 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
                    sans-serif;
                  color: #1a211e;
                  margin: 0 0 7px;
                "
                >State of residence <span aria-hidden="true " style="color: #1b2d5c">*</span></label
              >
              <div style="position: relative">
                <sc-raw-select
                  id="pr-state "
                  name="state "
                  aria-required="true "
                  aria-invalid="{{ ariaState }} "
                  aria-describedby="pr-state-err "
                  value="{{ stateVal }} "
                  sc-camel-on-change="{{ onState }} "
                  style="
                    display: block;
                    width: 100%;
                    font:
                      400 16px/1.4 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
                      sans-serif;
                    color: #1a211e;
                    background: #ffffff;
                    border: 1px solid #cfd3ce;
                    border-radius: 8px;
                    padding: 13px 40px 13px 14px;
                    appearance: none;
                    -webkit-appearance: none;
                    cursor: pointer;
                  "
                  style-focus="{ borderColor:'#1B2D5C', boxShadow:'0 0 0 3px rgba(27,45,92,0.18)' } "
                >
                  <option value=" " disabled=" ">Select your state</option>
                  <sc-for
                    list="{{ states }} "
                    as="st "
                  >
                    <option value="{{ st.name }} ">
                      {{ st.name }}
                    </option>
                  </sc-for>
                </sc-raw-select>
                <span
                  aria-hidden="true "
                  style="
                    position: absolute;
                    right: 15px;
                    top: 50%;
                    transform: translateY(-50%);
                    color: #565c58;
                    font-size: 11px;
                    pointer-events: none;
                  "
                  >▼</span
                >
              </div>
              <div
                value="{{ errState }} "
              >
                <p
                  id="pr-state-err "
                  role="alert "
                  style="
                    font:
                      500 13px/1.45 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
                      sans-serif;
                    color: #b42318;
                    margin: 7px 0 0;
                  "
                >
                  {{ errState }}
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <fieldset
              aria-describedby="pr-types-err "
              style="
                border: 0;
                margin: 0 0 20px;
                padding: 0;
                min-width: 0;
              "
            >
              <legend
                style="
                  display: block;
                  font:
                    600 14px/1.35 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
                    sans-serif;
                  color: #1a211e;
                  margin: 0 0 2px;
                  padding: 0;
                "
              >
                Request type
                <span aria-hidden="true " style="color: #1b2d5c">*</span>
              </legend>
              <p
                style="
                  font:
                    400 13px/1.45 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
                    sans-serif;
                  color: #656b67;
                  margin: 0 0 10px;
                "
              >
                Select at least one.
              </p>
              <div
                style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px"
              >
                <sc-for
                  list="{{ requestTypes }} "
                  as="rt "
                >
                  <label
                    for="{{ rt.id }} "
                    style="
                      display: flex;
                      align-items: flex-start;
                      gap: 12px;
                      padding: 13px 14px;
                      border: 1px solid #e2e4e0;
                      border-radius: 8px;
                      background: #ffffff;
                      cursor: pointer;
                      transition:
                        border-color 0.12s ease,
                        background 0.12s ease;
                    "
                    style-hover="{ borderColor:'#CFD3CE', background:'#FBFBFA' } "
                  >
                    <input
                      type="checkbox "
                      id="{{ rt.id }} "
                      name="request_type "
                      value="{{ rt.id }} "
                      checked="{{ rt.checked }} "
                      sc-camel-on-change="{{ rt.onToggle }} "
                      style="
                        width: 20px;
                        height: 20px;
                        margin: 1px 0 0;
                        accent-color: #1b2d5c;
                        flex: none;
                        cursor: pointer;
                      "
                    />
                    <span
                      style="
                        font:
                          400 15px/1.45 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
                          sans-serif;
                        color: #1a211e;
                      "
                    >
                      {{- rt.label -}}
                    </span>
                  </label>
                </sc-for>
              </div>
              <div
                value="{{ errTypes }} "
              >
                <p
                  id="pr-types-err "
                  role="alert "
                  style="
                    font:
                      500 13px/1.45 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
                      sans-serif;
                    color: #b42318;
                    margin: 10px 0 0;
                  "
                >
                  {{ errTypes }}
                </p>
              </div>
            </fieldset>
            <div style="margin-bottom: 26px">
              <label
                for="pr-details "
                style="
                  display: block;
                  font:
                    600 14px/1.35 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
                    sans-serif;
                  color: #1a211e;
                  margin: 0 0 7px;
                "
                >Additional details
                <span
                  style="
                    font-weight: 400;
                    color: #8a908c;
                    font-size: 13px;
                  "
                  >(optional)</span
                ></label
              >
              <textarea
                id="pr-details "
                name="details "
                rows="4 "
                value="{{ detailsVal }} "
                style="
                  display: block;
                  width: 100%;
                  font:
                    400 16px/1.5 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
                    sans-serif;
                  color: #1a211e;
                  background: #ffffff;
                  border: 1px solid #cfd3ce;
                  border-radius: 8px;
                  padding: 13px 14px;
                  min-height: 112px;
                  resize: vertical;
                "
                style-focus="{ borderColor:'#1B2D5C', boxShadow:'0 0 0 3px rgba(27,45,92,0.18)' } "
              ></textarea>
            </div>
            <button
              type="submit "
              style="
                appearance: none;
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 420px;
                display: inline-flex;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: center;
                gap: 8px;
                font:
                  600 16px/1 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
                  sans-serif;
                color: #ffffff;
                background: #1b2d5c;
                border: 1px solid #1b2d5c;
                border-radius: 8px;
                padding: 16px 24px;
                cursor: pointer;
                transition:
                  background 0.15s ease,
                  transform 0.06s ease;
              "
              style-hover="{ background:'#24386E', borderColor:'#24386E' } "
              style-active="{ transform:'translateY(1px)' } "
            >
              Submit request
            </button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        value="{{ showSubmitted }} "
      >
        <div
          id="form-confirm "
          tabindex="-1 "
          role="status "
          aria-live="polite "
          style="
            background: #eaeef6;
            border: 1px solid #c7d3e8;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 22px;
            animation: revEnter 0.25s ease both;
            outline: none;
          "
        >
          <div
            aria-hidden="true "
            style="
              display: inline-flex;
              align-items: center;
              justify-content: center;
              width: 30px;
              height: 30px;
              border-radius: 999px;
              background: #1b2d5c;
              color: #ffffff;
              font:
                700 15px/1 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
                sans-serif;
              margin-bottom: 12px;
            "
          >
            ✓
          </div>
          <h3
            style="
              font:
                600 18px/1.3 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
                sans-serif;
              color: #1a211e;
              margin: 0 0 8px;
            "
          >
            Request received
          </h3>
          <p
            style="
              font:
                400 15px/1.6 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
                sans-serif;
              color: #353b37;
              margin: 0;
              max-width: 60ch;
            "
          >
            Your request has been received. We will verify and respond within 45 days to the email you provided. If we
            need more time as permitted by law, we will let you know within that window.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <div
      aria-hidden="true "
      style="height: 1px; background: #e2e4e0; margin: 36px 0 24px"
    ></div>
    <p
      style="
        font:
          400 14px/1.65 &quot;Hanken Grotesk&quot;,
          sans-serif;
        color: #565c58;
        margin: 0;
        max-width: 64ch;
      "
    >
      Requests can also be made by emailing
      <a href="mailto:support@reviveteeth.com ">support@reviveteeth.com</a>. For full details on what we collect, how we
      use it, and your rights, see our <a href="/pages/privacy-policy ">Privacy Policy</a>. Exercising your privacy
      rights will never affect your order, pricing, or the service you receive.
    </p>
  </main>
  <footer style="border-top: 1px solid #e2e4e0; background: #f4f5f7">
    <nav
      aria-label="Policies "
      style="
        max-width: 688px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 24px 24px 40px;
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 12px 22px;
      "
    >
      <a
        href="/pages/privacy-policy "
        class="privacy-links"
        >Privacy Policy</a
      >
      <a
        href="/pages/terms-of-service "
        class="privacy-links"
        >Terms of Service</a
      >
      <a
        href="/pages/refund-remake-returns-policy "
        class="privacy-links"
        >Refund, Remake and Returns Policy</a
      >
      <a
        href="/pages/shipping-policy "
        class="privacy-links"
        >Shipping Policy</a
      >
      <a
        href="/pages/disclaimer "
        class="privacy-links"
        >Disclaimer</a
      >
      <a
        href="/pages/privacy-opt-out "
        aria-current="page "
        class="privacy-links"
        >Do Not Sell or Share My Personal Information</a
      >
    </nav>
  </footer>


</div>
